title: Renovated 2 BED 2 BATH APARTMENT NEXT TO COSTCO AND BART
posting_body: ['Call Us Today', 'show contact info', 'Come enjoy your own beautifully designed and spacious home.', 'Every piece of furniture will find a home here and your sleek, open kitchen offers plenty of room for your dinner parties and entertaining.', "When it's all said and down settle in with a book in either of two deep soak bathtubs.", 'You new home also includes washer and dryer, walk in closets, and your own covered garage parking.', 'Enjoy the convenience of the neighbor!', "Step out your door and shop Trader Joe's, Costco, grab a cup of coffee at Starbucks, bank at Chase Bank, and more.", 'Bring your delicious bargains home and get you grill on in our barbecue and picnic areas followed by a dip in our large and toasty Jacuzzi.', 'Impress your friends with your luxurious apartment in a beautiful, polished and well situated community!', 'Office Hours', 'Monday: Closed', 'Tuesday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Wednesday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Thursday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Friday: 10:00 AM - 06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM - 05:00 PM', 'Sunday: Closed', 'South City Station Apartments', '101 McLellan Drive', 'More Photos', '<URL>']
